title: Seeing Yourself The Way You Want To Be | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Seeing Yourself The Way You Want To Be | Joel Osteen
description:
How you see yourself can determine the kind of life you're going to live. If you want to be successful, start by picturing yourself as a victor. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
